    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she looks like she just rolled off the showroom floor! This car has been pampered since day one\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful brand-new feel. If you're looking for total perfection, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed!",
