    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the rod bearings have been proactively replaced, the VANOS system has been fully overhauled with Beisan components, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014addressing the three critical concerns of the chassis. The suspension geometry remains tight with fresh bushings and factory-spec dampers, ensuring the limited-slip differential translates every horse-power to the tarmac with precision. Zero aesthetic compromises, no dead pixels, and a pristine undercarriage. This is a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
