    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. I have babied this car since day one, and it is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels just like it did when it first left the showroom floor! It\u2019s been kept spotless, runs like a dream, and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for the road, this is the one. Drop me a message, I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
